        "action": "Don't allow people to vote by post ",
        "additional_details": "We believe the postal voting system is open to cheating, and therefore needs to be banned.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to stop allowing people to vote via a postal vote and to fund more measures to ensure voting stations are monitored and secure during elections.",
